 Sydney, a young, blind violinist is given the chance to see for the first    
 time since childhood through a miraculous corneal transplant. As Sydney      
 adjusts to a dizzying new world of colors and shapes, she is haunted by      
 frightening visions of death itself capturing the doomed and dragging them   
 away from the world of the living. Terrorized and on the brink of insanity,  
 Sydney must discover whose eyes she has inherited, and what secret visions
